T1  - Ability-Satisfaction Relationships: Field and Laboratory Studies
AU  - Barrett, Gerald V.
AU  - Forbes, J. Benjamin
AU  - O'Connor, Edward J.
AU  - Alexander, Ralph A.
Y1  - 1980/09/01
PY  - 1980
DA  - 1980/09/01
